OL,3,CUK needs 'reckoning with Government
OL,4,Cspending', Treasury minister will say
OL,6,FThe UK is "long overdue a reckoning
OL,7,Fwith Government spending", a senior
OL,8,FTreasury minister will say as Labour
OL,9,Ffaces the prospect of making further
OL,10,Fcuts.
OL,12,FDarren Jones, the Chief Secretary to
OL,13,Fthe Treasury, is expected to use a
OL,14,Fspeech at the Institute for
OL,15,FGovernment's annual conference on
OL,16,FTuesday to argue that ministers need a
OL,17,Fdifferent approach to ensure
OL,18,Ftaxpayers' money is spent effectively.
