OL,3,CUK needs 'reckoning with Government
OL,4,Cspending', Treasury minister will say
OL,6,FAs Chief Secretary, Mr Jones is
OL,7,Fresponsible for assessing ministers'
OL,8,Frequests for cash and has announced he
OL,9,Fwill adopt a "zero-based" approach
OL,10,Fthat requires every pound the
OL,11,FGovernment spends to be fully
OL,12,Fjustified.
OL,14,FThis could become a tough process.
OL,15,FMinisters have already been told to
OL,16,Ffind efficiency savings worth 5% of
OL,17,Ftheir departments' budgets, but the
OL,18,Frising cost of borrowing could mean
OL,19,Feven steeper cuts are required if the
OL,20,FGovernment is to meet the fiscal rules
OL,21,Fit has set itself.
