OL,3,CUK needs 'reckoning with Government
OL,4,Cspending', Treasury minister will say
OL,6,FThe alternatives ` greater borrowing
OL,7,For more tax increases ` have been
OL,8,Feffectively ruled out by Chancellor
OL,9,FRachel Reeves.
OL,11,FMr Jones is expected to defend this
OL,12,Fapproach on Tuesday, saying: "We are
OL,13,Flong overdue a reckoning with
OL,14,FGovernment spending, and a realistic
OL,15,Fappraisal of how we are using
OL,16,Ftaxpayers' money."
